{"tid":2165395,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–植物的「體味」","createTime":"2020-08-19T20:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T00:46:43.000Z","uid":38861,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d827620ff3e548bede55b029478cc9e86bb4ed","tid":2165395,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:01:55.000Z","msg":"上一篇的深入淺出講述了人體的體味，緊接以來的這一篇將會講述一下大自然界的「體味」互動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/468715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F468715&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=8ef11bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/468715</a><br />\n<br />\n適者生存，弱肉強食，一向被喻為大自然界的法則。<br />\n植物作為食物鏈的最底層，大多時候也逃不過被食物鏈上層生物侵食的局面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMrFi8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMrFi8L.jpg&h=c7af6bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖1為毛蟲獵食樹葉的畫面，這棵植物並不是捕蠅草系列，看起上來的確沒有任何反擊或防禦的手段，任人魚肉。<br />\n<br />\n但實情其實並非如此。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/150reG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F150reG8.jpg&h=10437b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖2為椿象從後出現，反過來獵食毛蟲的畫面。然而，椿象的出現並不是偶然，而是植物暗中「召喚」而來的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETi03Ay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETi03Ay.jpg&h=3d34c9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖3，當樹葉收到傷害的時候，它們會即時釋放出一堆統稱為 Green Leave Volatiles(GLV)的化合物（Ref1)，這個情況下，毛蟲的口水包含著一些物質，會將這些GLV化合物由Z形態轉化成為E形態；<br />\n<br />\n這物質究竟是甚麼，科學家暫時還沒清楚，只是知道該物質在高溫下便會失效。<br />\n<br />\nZ形態及E形態是化學用詞，用在描述化學物的形態。<br />\n<br />\n強硬來說的話，Z形態就是用胡蘿蔔當作雙耳、樹枝當作雙手的雪人。<br />\n而E形態就是用樹枝當作雙耳、胡蘿蔔當作雙手的雪人。<br />\n<br />\n大家所組成的元素均是一樣，但位置上卻有著不同的地方。<br />\n<br />\n我並沒有能力再以更深入淺出的方式解釋，有興趣的話可以自行Google。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBZogVC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBZogVC.jpg&h=1ac35aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖4）對於椿象來說， E形態的GLV是一種非常強大的吸引劑，亦因而被吸引前來，反咬毛蟲。<br />\n<br />\n所以整件事情的來龍去脈，就是毛蟲傷害樹葉的時候，其口水觸化樹葉裡頭的摔發性化學物轉變，其轉變的化合物吸引捕食毛蟲的獵人前來，因而「間接」地救了樹葉一命。<br />\n<br />\n在這裡必須強調的是，這種關係是物種針對性的。<br />\n<br />\n科學家在一篇學術文章（Ref1)證實，若果毛蟲品種並不是圖1列明的那一個品種，其口水是不會觸發樹葉化合物Z到E的轉變。<br />\n<br />\n植物是否會用不同的方式應付不同品種的入侵者，這暫時還是未知之數。<br />\n但至少圖1-4的物種互動已有科學證據支持，由此已經可以看得出大自然物種之間的互動是絕非簡單的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站<span class=\"blue\">科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=6e3cdacd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=2a389bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科普資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/329/5995/1075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F329%2F5995%2F1075&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufV%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=f94463ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/329/5995/1075</a>"},{"pid":"6410e6a5c5bd56d568144cc2e3850b83c04d9112","tid":2165395,"uid":2776,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:02:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜都出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5f5fb06112194d3fef65a13340326b800d33c4","tid":2165395,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6410e6a5c5bd56d568144cc2e3850b83c04d9112","tid":2165395,"uid":2776,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:02:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜都出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:03:39.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69c5bb45347fb02387f6da86356c797b3e7bcf3","tid":2165395,"uid":2776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d5f5fb06112194d3fef65a13340326b800d33c4","tid":2165395,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6410e6a5c5bd56d568144cc2e3850b83c04d9112","tid":2165395,"uid":2776,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:02:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜都出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:03:39.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:05:36.000Z","msg":"4點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推埋就瞓"},{"pid":"5b32f7d3f444f06b34d668163c8b41fdc84214df","tid":2165395,"uid":131621,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cecb5b741f17007ff1253d59219dffc5dc13621","tid":2165395,"uid":300542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T20:26:46.000Z","msg":"E 同 Z 係 cis-tra